// Placeholder rnnoise.wasm.
// This file exists only to avoid 404 responses when the RNNoise AudioWorklet
// tries to fetch `/rnnoise.wasm`. The actual WebAssembly noise suppression
// binary should be provided here in real deployments.
//
// WebAssembly.instantiate() will fail on this text content, and the
// RNNoise processor in `public/audio-worklets/rnnoise-processor.js` will
// fall back to passthrough mode (no noise suppression), which is acceptable
// behaviour when the real WASM is not available.
